Do not upload the automatically generated cache folder:

```text
__pycache__/
```

Recommended `.gitignore` entries:

```gitignore
__pycache__/
*.pyc
```

## Technical Scope

This Python package provides an independent implementation of the analytical and Monte Carlo model. It supports reproducibility and cross-verification with MATLAB.

The current scope includes coverage, density, normalized capacity, node qualification, and independent-link multi-connectivity reliability. It does not currently include traffic queues, correlated failures, mobility, heterogeneous radio access, or protocol-level signaling.

